{"tid":2440582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人力挺台灣鳳梨銷量升5倍 水果店老闆：紙箱不夠用","createTime":"2021-03-10T05:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T11:17:06.000Z","uid":337052,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f9df3e7f2d2567a0b590342fcdbf212ffc01359b","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">港人力挺台灣鳳梨銷量升5倍 水果店老闆：紙箱不夠用</span></strong><br />\n更新時間： 2021/03/08 00:16<br />\n<br />\n台灣鳳梨遭中國封殺，卻在香港成為熱門話題，許多香港人認為這是中國不合理的政治打壓，特別在此時訂購台灣鳳梨捧場，用現金「懲罰」台灣鳳梨。<br />\n<br />\n香港黃大仙林記水果店主林先生表示，台灣鳳梨的合格率超過99%，而且中國聲稱台灣鳳梨有介殼蟲，其實本身中國大陸也有害蟲，<span class=\"red\">「海南島出產的水果，害蟲性的比率反而更高卻沒有被禁，因此會有不少人覺得這是政治考慮。」</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣鳳梨突然被禁，令大批香港人想要「下架」台灣鳳梨。林先生說：「今年鳳梨還沒到貨，就已經有不少人致電來想訂貨。往年鳳梨的需求不多，但單是這星期，銷量已經是去年的5倍，不知不覺已向台灣訂了約二百箱金鑽鳳梨。台灣那邊做到打電話來說，<span class=\"red\">指現在不是沒有鳳梨，只是沒有紙箱。</span>」不過林先生強調目前的台灣鳳梨，質量還沒到最佳狀態，「剛開季的水果價錢會較高，質量還沒到最佳狀態，<span class=\"red\">到四月開始，是鳳梨出口的高峰期，品質會較高，而且運去大陸的鳳梨無法出口，供應量上升，價錢也會下降。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/SgFhinPsbr2bD0UDJjOQlTNO0Ms=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HLLHW5H7FFDELEBMQSYXXQMGEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSgFhinPsbr2bD0UDJjOQlTNO0Ms%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHLLHW5H7FFDELEBMQSYXXQMGEM.jpg&h=2079ee5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水果店老闆透露，過去一周台灣鳳梨銷量暴增。香港《飲食男女》<a href=\"http://etw.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fetw.hk&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4a46bb65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">etw.hk</a>提供<br />\n<br />\n林先生認為台灣10億新台幣補助方案，可能會讓某些無良農民乘機撈錢，「因為台灣有十億補助方案，本身是一件好事，想要補貼農民，但出一箱鳳梨會有補貼的話，一定會有人不斷地出貨，不管鳳梨已經成熟了沒有。」若想要選好的鳳梨，林先生建議香港消費者買空運抵港貨為佳，因為選擇空運的商家，一般比較捨得花錢買品質，待鳳梨七至八成熟才收割，風味較佳；而船運的鳳梨，可能只有兩至四成熟就去收割，<span class=\"red\">前者每個售價約$40至$60港幣（144-216元台幣），後者則約$20至$30（72-108元台幣），單看價錢已知分別。</span>而且鳳梨的熟度，在收割當下已經斷定，因此若想要買便宜貨再去催熟，也無法做到理想的甜度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/o_xl1A1fsXJFUpYYNpDVUEWSWKs=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GEYUPGSEDJCE7CBJHBJISR4AUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo_xl1A1fsXJFUpYYNpDVUEWSWKs%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGEYUPGSEDJCE7CBJHBJISR4AUA.jpg&h=7ebed388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港主要進口台灣三種鳳梨，<span class=\"red\">以台農17號金鑽鳳梨最多。</span>香港《飲食男女》<a href=\"http://etw.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fetw.hk&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4a46bb65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">etw.hk</a>提供<br />\n菠蘿葉像鳳尾 台灣人取名為鳳梨<br />\n<br />\n香港稱為菠蘿，台灣卻稱鳳梨，引來網上有不少人展開關於「鳳梨」及「菠蘿」的討論，探討兩者有否不同。林先生說：「因為台灣人認為菠蘿葉的尾很像鳳尾，於是將其稱為鳳梨，不少人以為是兩種水果，但兩者屬同一植物科，就如不同水果都有分不同地區、產地一樣。」其實亞洲地區的菠蘿大部份都是奎恩種，當年台灣有一種叫作本島仔鳳梨的奎恩種菠蘿，直到日治時代，日本人想要製作罐頭菠蘿，但菠蘿本身釘眼深，去除麻煩而肉又較少，因此日本人找來肉較多，而且處理較方便的開英種鳳梨引入台灣，並禁止台灣人繼續種本島仔鳳梨。當時有農民不滿，<span class=\"red\">因此帶着本島仔鳳梨去沖繩石垣島種植，慢慢的演變成現在沖繩有名的釋迦鳳梨</span>，而當年引入的開英種鳳梨，就慢慢變成現在常見的台灣鳳梨之一。長久發展以來，菠蘿和鳳梨也有少許分別，<span class=\"red\">菠蘿容易令人覺得刺口，加上菠蘿含有有機酶和蛋白酸</span>，有不少人對這兩種成份敏感，因此需要泡鹽水，去除大部份過敏成份。相反，<span class=\"red\">鳳梨則沒有令人刺口的感覺。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/yzwiLZpDsRoQeL0oAgbkDueWB9I=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WVIOXQ3MOBHMZCEMQICLFMGRKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyzwiLZpDsRoQeL0oAgbkDueWB9I%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWVIOXQ3MOBHMZCEMQICLFMGRKU.jpg&h=2f0696b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冷藏的鳳梨可頭尾倒置讓甜度一致。香港《飲食男女》<a href=\"http://etw.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fetw.hk&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4a46bb65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">etw.hk</a>提供<br />\n<br />\n倒轉鳳梨放置 使甜度一致<br />\n<br />\n直到現在，雖然台灣有二十多種不同品種，但出口香港最主要有三種，分別是台農17號金鑽鳳梨、台農20號牛奶鳳梨，以及近年新興、有鳳梨界的巨無霸之稱的西瓜鳳梨。要挑選優質鳳梨，林先生表示，除了最好買$40港幣以上的空運貨，亦要看看葉是否青綠色，底部及肉身按下去不要過熟，如果符合以上條件，鳳梨基本上都是優質。另外他還指點一招，因為完熟鳳梨運輸到香港後，已經冷藏了一段時間，買回家後，最好放在室溫半天，等它醒過來，而且切之前，可以先將整個鳳梨上下倒轉放置15分鐘，讓沉底的糖分倒流，使整個鳳梨的甜度一致。切割時，可以將鳳梨的頭尾部位切去，再像切蘋果一般，切開幾份然後去皮；亦可將四邊直接切去，不過這樣就會切走不少果肉。（香港《飲食男女》<a href=\"http://etw.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fetw.hk&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4a46bb65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">etw.hk</a>／提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/uZN2-w8AxUsK2JpdDLp6ewSzKqs=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W2TEL5JWHVEBZHATRW5Q24GVLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuZN2-w8AxUsK2JpdDLp6ewSzKqs%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW2TEL5JWHVEBZHATRW5Q24GVLU.jpg&h=182f6fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210308/S2O5Q6QQ7JA6DH5WWHL3YMG6DI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210308%2FS2O5Q6QQ7JA6DH5WWHL3YMG6DI%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=55a56799\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210308%2FS2O5Q6QQ7JA6DH5WWHL3YMG6DI%2F&h=60f9de58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210308/S2O5Q6QQ7JA6DH5WWHL3YMG6DI/</a>"},{"pid":"55074ff289563d62779669d59c2d5fdb561f405a","tid":2440582,"uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"台獨係香港好有市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7f622101ced1671397ff87ded5c157e37e7b72","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:03:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/268335023528293/posts/1351897071838744/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F268335023528293%2Fposts%2F1351897071838744%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=ba3d2293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/268335023528293/posts/1351897071838744/</a><br />\n日本貨好友站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/156315858254515/posts/822552411630853/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F156315858254515%2Fposts%2F822552411630853%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=05d04ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/156315858254515/posts/822552411630853/?d=n</a><br />\n豪記蔬果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BrosFruit/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBrosFruit%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=d1909d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BrosFruit/</a><br />\n巴打鮮菓"},{"pid":"a5ac6633ff7cbf507d48652f7ad97759f7a10c33","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"55074ff289563d62779669d59c2d5fdb561f405a","tid":2440582,"uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"台獨係香港好有市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"台灣人也支持港獨"},{"pid":"e8a253039d4fc0424e2135a605dd096e9c528ff4","tid":2440582,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"叫中國禁埋紙箱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09959b1cf9d12b8b3c24b3d6c02a6807196e3ccc","tid":2440582,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6483782adc6f1d80d3f6b7ee50476054f94ccc","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DrFruitsHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDrFruitsHK%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=aa940b73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DrFruitsHK/</a><br />\nDr. Fruits 水果博士"},{"pid":"f83a037bfcd36d2708e16200ba9cc17d2c699811","tid":2440582,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"全部都要"},{"pid":"b31ac469369b260af44424eab6286c872a98d814","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8a253039d4fc0424e2135a605dd096e9c528ff4","tid":2440582,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"叫中國禁埋紙箱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"紙箱是台灣製造"},{"pid":"2ad2046d25b2fa9bffbc9e4e20e7ee6b52466b76","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83a037bfcd36d2708e16200ba9cc17d2c699811","tid":2440582,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"全部都要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"謝謝"},{"pid":"5652ffec99a4967ba49082c2c80f2753e3b38b47","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"巴打鮮菓<br />\n3月8日下午3:37  &middot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-3.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/158636491_858570294992314_369626463290477981_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=PyRuR98ZPIgAX-QDg7k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-3.fna&amp;oh=8febb6ec57cc211709b4230749b49bb9&amp;oe=606ED488\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-3.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F158636491_858570294992314_369626463290477981_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DPyRuR98ZPIgAX-QDg7k%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-3.fna%26oh%3D8febb6ec57cc211709b4230749b49bb9%26oe%3D606ED488&h=e0226350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df58c17f5c8887921069679456c0713222022752","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pFjgjgCY_Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpFjgjgCY_Ew&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=7d99d682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pFjgjgCY_Ew</a>"},{"pid":"74d58fc599f92fff72f5c1a769ffdedbd9c6d170","tid":2440582,"uid":153956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"比香港往年多5倍, 夠唔夠中國無左既1%?"},{"pid":"355a2e499d7663cb031b684f11e78d2928ce3e27","tid":2440582,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"豪記蔬果<br />\n昨天上午4:19  &middot; <br />\n開左門喇🥱<br />\n<br />\n台灣金鑽鳳梨5/6/7/8/9裝<br />\n$160/箱<br />\n<br />\n散買<br />\n$35/個（5裝<br />\n$20/個（9裝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/158105989_827676934451734_8421750906004241978_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=uIiNuwGj5ekAX_e88kW&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-4.fna&amp;oh=1fc826501bebec4a246f0e747f6aa4eb&amp;oe=606E5247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F158105989_827676934451734_8421750906004241978_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DuIiNuwGj5ekAX_e88kW%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-4.fna%26oh%3D1fc826501bebec4a246f0e747f6aa4eb%26oe%3D606E5247&h=1c883a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"